              <div class="thumbnail"><a href="http://www.xiatao.com/1208.html" title="【第一现场】我们来郑州分享啦！" target="_blank"><img width="280" height="180" src="http://www.xiatao.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/1041321222-280x180.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="1041321222" /></a></div>
